 "blurb": "Destruction Warlock is TBC's endgame caster king: Shadow Bolt machine-gunning with the Improved Shadow Bolt debuff feeding every other warlock's damage too. The spec's phase curve is the steepest in the game — mediocre in Karazhan gear, untouchable in Sunwell. This Phase 1 snapshot aggregates 390 top DPS parses from Karazhan, Gruul's Lair and Magtheridon; the highest-consensus pick is Spellstrike Pants at 87% usage.",
